Class UseCase2

java.lang.Object
testsuites.UseCase2
class UseCase2
extends java.lang.Object
## Use Case 2: Run Program ### Main Success Scenario 1. User presses F5 2. Next block is highlighted 3. User presses F5 4. Highlighted block is executed repeat steps 2, 3 and 4 until program is finished. ### Extensions 1a. Program Area does not contain exactly one connected block group. 1. Execution does not start. 1b. Program Area contains a condition block. 1. Execution does not start. 1b. Program Area contains a surrounding block without condition. 1. Execution does not start
